name: Password Depot 6 File
summary: Learn about .PSW6 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: PSW6 files use a master password, a key file, or both, to protect all information. The software encrypts the information and only allows it to be decrypted with the master password and/or key file.
NOTE: Password Depot versions 3-5 store use the .PSW extension.

description: File created by Password Depot 6, a password manager for Windows, Android, and iOS; saves a collection of personal passwords; can also store user names, credit card information, software licenses, importance levels, and other related information.
